ğŸš€ Complete GitHub Integration Hub - Project Concept
Core Feature Modules
1. Git Operations Manager
Push/Pull/Sync Dashboard
Real-time branch visualization
Commit history timeline with diff previews
Conflict resolution interface
Multi-repo batch operations
Git stash manager
Reserve/Revert System
Snapshot creation before risky operations
One-click rollback to any commit
Branch comparison view
Cherry-pick assistant
2. Repository File Manager
Smart Backup System
Automated periodic backups (configurable schedule)
Incremental backup with deduplication
Backup compression & encryption
Cloud storage integration (optional: S3, Google Drive)
Restore points with metadata (tags, descriptions)
File Explorer
Multi-pane file browser (local + remote repos)
Drag-and-drop between repos
File search across all backed-up repos
Preview for common file types (md, json, images)
Bulk operations (rename, move, delete)
3. Integrated Code Editor (IDE Lite)
Monaco Editor Integration (VS Code's editor engine)
Syntax highlighting for 50+ languages
IntelliSense/autocomplete
Multi-tab editing
Split view support
Git Integration
Inline diff view
Commit directly from editor
Blame annotations
Stage/unstage hunks visually
4. Pastebin Feature
Code Snippet Manager
Create public/private pastes
GitHub Gist integration (auto-sync)
Syntax highlighting
Expiration timers
Share links with password protection
Embed code snippets in docs
Snippet Library
Tag-based organization
Search with filters
Version history for pastes
Fork/clone snippets
5. GitHub Actions Dashboard
Workflow Control Center
Visual workflow builder (YAML generator)
Trigger workflows manually
Real-time build logs
Artifact downloads
Re-run failed jobs
Analytics
Build success/failure trends
Execution time charts
Cost tracking (Actions minutes)
Notifications for failures
6. Codespaces Manager
Codespace Lifecycle Control
Create/start/stop/delete codespaces
Pre-built configuration templates
Resource usage monitoring
Port forwarding management
Quick Access
One-click launch in browser
Recent codespaces list
Auto-shutdown scheduler
ğŸ—ï¸ Suggested Tech Stack
typescript
// Frontend
- React 18 + TypeScript
- Vite (fast builds)
- Tailwind CSS + Framer Motion (animations)
- Monaco Editor (@monaco-editor/react)
- Shadcn UI components
// State Management
- Zustand or Jotai (lightweight)
- TanStack Query (API caching)
// Backend/API
- Octokit (GitHub REST + GraphQL API)
- GitHub Apps Authentication
- Node.js/Express API layer (optional)
// Storage
- IndexedDB (local repo metadata)
- Supabase/Firebase (backup metadata + user data)
- S3-compatible storage (actual backups)
